---
const credentials = [
  { year: "2008", title: "Licenciatura en Psicología", institution: "Universidad de Granada" },
  { year: "2010", title: "Máster en Psicología Clínica", institution: "Universidad de Málaga" },
  { year: "2015", title: "Especialización en Terapia de Pareja", institution: "EFT" },
  { year: "Actualidad", title: "Formación continua", institution: "Tercera generación" },
];
---

<section class="section bg-bg-base relative overflow-hidden" id="sobre-mi">
  <div class="absolute top-1/2 right-0 w-[40vw] h-[40vw] bg-sage/5 rounded-full blur-[120px] -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2 pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <div class="container-elegant relative z-10">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-stretch">
      <div class="relative order-2 lg:order-1 opacity-0 min-h-[500px] lg:min-h-0" data-animate>
        <div class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 w-full h-full border border-sage/20 rounded-t-full rounded-b-3xl hidden lg:block pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 w-3/4 h-3/4 bg-sage/10 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></div>

        <div class="relative w-full h-full min-h-[400px] lg:min-h-[500px] overflow-hidden rounded-t-full rounded-b-3xl shadow-2xl shadow-sage/10">
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551836022-d5d88e9218df?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80"
            alt="María Ángeles Mata - Psicóloga en Córdoba con más de 15 años de experiencia"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale-[10%] hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-1000 hover:scale-105"
            width="400"
            height="500"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
        
        <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 lg:right-auto lg:-left-6 bg-bg-surface p-5 rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-border-light max-w-[240px]">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-sage/30 mb-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z"/>
          </svg>
          <p class="font-serif text-text-primary italic leading-relaxed text-sm">"La terapia es un viaje conjunto hacia el bienestar"</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="order-1 lg:order-2 opacity-0 flex flex-col justify-center py-4" data-animate style="animation-delay: 0.15s">
        <div class="section-label mb-5 w-fit">
          <div class="w-4 h-px bg-sage"></div>
          <span class="eyebrow !mb-0 text-xs">Sobre mí</span>
        </div>

        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl lg:text-4xl text-text-primary mb-5 leading-tight">
          Tu psicóloga en <span class="text-sage italic font-light">Córdoba</span>
        </h2>

        <div class="space-y-4 text-body mb-8">
          <p>
            Soy María Ángeles Mata, psicóloga colegiada con más de 15 años de experiencia ayudando a personas a superar sus dificultades emocionales y recuperar el bienestar.
          </p>
          <p>
            Mi enfoque combina la rigurosidad científica con un trato humano y cercano. Creo firmemente que la terapia es un espacio colaborativo donde exploramos juntos qué te bloquea y construimos herramientas efectivas.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-8">
          <span class="text-xs text-text-tertiary uppercase tracking-wider mb-3 block">Formación académica</span>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            {credentials.map((cred) => (
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-2 bg-bg-surface rounded-lg border border-border-light hover:border-sage/30 transition-colors cursor-default">
                <span class="text-xs font-medium text-sage">{cred.year}</span>
                <span class="text-sm text-text-primary">{cred.title}</span>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>

        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary w-fit">
          <span>Conóceme en consulta</span>
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M17.25 8.75L21 12m0 0l-3.75 3.25M21 12H3" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
